>\n                        </a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"interview/#ohta\">\n                            <img class=\"img\" src=\"images/interview-pic06.jpg\">\n                            <div>\n                                <p><span>栄養士</span>2012年入社</p>\n                                <p>太田 千尋<span>CHIHIRO OTA</span></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"interview/#ozaki\">\n                            <img class=\"img\" src=\"images/interview-pic07.jpg\">\n                            <div>\n                                <p><span>事務管理</span>2011年入社</p>\n                                <p>尾﨑 祐文<span>YOSHIFUMI OZAKI</span></p>\n                            </div>\n                        </a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </section>\n\n\n\n\n        </div><!-- /#content_area -->\n\n\n        <!-- ▼ FOOTER start\n################################################## -->\n<a class=\"side_cv\" href=\"/recruit/entry/\">\n\t<img src=\"/recruit/common_img/float_pc.png\" class=\"rwd_disp_ox\">\n\t<img src=\"/recruit/common_img/float_sp.png\" class=\"rwd_disp_xo\">\n</a>\n<div class=\"contact\">\n\t<p>エントリーをご希望の方は<br class=\"rwd_disp_xo\">こちらから</p>\n\t<a class=\"arrow-tin-wh\" href=\"/recruit/entry/\">エントリーフォーム</a>\n</div>\n\n<footer id=\"footer\">\n\t<div class=\"footer--top\">\n\t\t<div class=\"site_wrap\">\n\t\t\t<a class=\"footer--top_logo\">\n\t\t\t    <img class=\"img\" src=\"/recruit/common_img/logo.png\" alt=\"舞浜倶楽部\">\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"footer--top_address\">舞浜倶楽部 本社　<br class=\"rwd_disp_xo\">〒279-0023 千葉県浦安市⾼洲1-2-1</p>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"tel\">TEL：<a class=\"sp_link\" href=\"tel:047-304-2400\">047-304-2400</a></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"footer--bottom site_wrap\">\n        <div class=\"footer--bottom_link\">\n            <p><a class=\"cp_btn arrow-tin-wh\" href=\"//www.maihamaclub.co.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">株式会社舞